------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VERSION 1.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - added --force option to the up, down, and latest commands; this will
      force the script to continue execution despite any migration errors that
      occur
    - added run command to allow the execution of a single migration

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VERSION 1.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - fixed bug: when migration scripts are removed, the script will now
      remove the entry from the database tracking table; this should stop
      missing file exceptions when running the up, down, or latest commands
    - fixed bug: when running init, an exception was thrown if the 
      db_config.php was missing or PDO was unable to connect to the database

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VERSION 1.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - fixed interleaving so it doesn't roll back before rolling back up
    - added ability to remove all migrations by doing ./migrate.php down 0

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VERSION 1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - now stores migration information in database table;
    - supports migration interleaving (insertion of migrations between 
      migrations which have already been run)
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
VERSION 1.0 (First Release)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	- able to initialize migrations via command line prompts
	- integrated help system
	- able to migrate to latest, up to a specific migration, or down to a 
	  specific migration
	- able to list all migrations
	- able to get status
	- able to add new migrations